</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Water (from the natural springs at University High School) can be used for a 
fish pond where students could go fishing (Plugging the Leak, Westside, March 
13, 1994).If the water is cold enough, it could be stocked with trout. More 
