not seriously affected and were reportedly able to continue to care for the 
youngster. 
</P>
<P>
 Fumes emanating from the body of a cancer patient brought to a Riverside 
County hospital recently overcame medical workers, some of whom had to be 
hospitalized. That case is still under investigation. 
