</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A no-host business luncheon for Lancaster City Council candidate Deborah 
Shelton will be held at noon today at Cifarelli's restaurant, 43953 15th St. 
West, Lancaster. Reservations: (805) 946-1393 or (805) 942-3975. 
</P>
<P>
 A fund-raiser for James H. Gilmartin, who is running in the 25th Congressional 
District Democratic primary, will be held from noon to 1:30 p.m. and from 6 to 
7 p.m. today at the Santa Clarita Brewing Co., 20655 Soledad Canyon Road, 
Canyon Country. Twenty percent of the food sales will be donated to Gilmartin's 
campaign. Participants need to pick up a green flyer in advance at the United 
Democratic Headquarters, 20611 Soledad Canyon Road. Information: (805) 
251-8484. 
