<P>
 New Trustees -- The Long Beach-based Community Rehabilitation Industries 
Foundation has named three new trustees: Long Beach attorney George Kelly, 
housing manager Dorothy Hicks and the Rev. Christopher Lenocker, associate 
pastor of Long Beach Presbyterian Covenant Church. The organization was 
identified incorrectly in the People column March 10. 
